data.description: Nestled in the serene neighborhood of Wolf Ranch, this charming home is a perfect blend of comfort & convenience. With its picturesque surroundings & thoughtful design, this property offers an ideal retreat for those seeking a harmonious lifestyle. This home boasts ample space for your family to grow & thrive. The open-concept living area provides a seamless flow between the kitchen, dining, & living spaces, making it an entertainer's dream. The kitchen is a culinary delight with top-of-the-line appliances, granite countertops, and plenty of storage space. The owners bedroom is a sanctuary of relaxation, featuring an ensuite bathroom & a walk-in closet. Step outside to your backyard oasis, where you can enjoy the Colorado sunshine on the spacious patio or explore the beautifully landscaping. Conveniently located near schools, parks, shopping centers, major transportation routes & military bases, this home offers the perfect blend of tranquility & accessibility. As part of the Wolf Ranch community, residents have access to a fishing pond, clubhouse, playgrounds & parks/trails. This is a must see & won't last!
